title: Stanklepus - Not That Crazy (Chicago House, EDM, Minimal House)
description:
New Track bordering somewhere between Chicago House and Minimal House.

Found an old voicemail from a 'friend' of mine, and thought the vocals were a perfect addition to the feel of the track. Shout out to my brain, for always remembering to document, save, and use life experiences to experiment and create art in all mediums.

Spread the love, positive vibes, and seed for your fellow pirates
